        "The husband and wife were arrested by the Badulla Police yesterday morning with stolen goods worth 20 lakh rupees.",
        "The 60-year-old husband and his 57-year-old wife have been arrested, according to the Badulla Police.",
        "Police have recovered stolen cooking gas cylinders, cooking gas stoves, electrical appliances, musical instruments and shoes from the suspects' house in Pahalawatta, Badulla.",
        "Police are investigating a case of a couple using a young man addicted to drugs and committing theft, and police are investigating the arrest of the youth involved."
